---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Free Tax & Debt Calculators — S-Corp, Buy Borrow Die, Debt Payoff | TaxDebtWealthSuite"
  description="Three free financial calculators: S-Corp vs sole trader tax optimizer, Buy Borrow Die / SBLOC strategy modeler, and debt snowball vs avalanche planner. US, UK, Canada, Australia."
  ogImage="https://taxdebtwealthsuite.com/images/og-home.png"
>
  <!-- Hero / Intro Section -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-20 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest bg-[#00F5D4]/10 text-[#00F5D4] border border-[#00F5D4]/20 mb-6">
      Strategic Financial Modeling
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tight leading-none font-sans">
      Free Tax, Debt &amp; Wealth Strategy Calculators
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Free, professional-grade interactive calculators designed to model advanced tax strategies, run multi-method debt payoffs, and optimize leverage risk.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Large Cards / CTAs Grid -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Card 1: Buy, Borrow, Die -->
      <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-[#00F5D4]/40 transition-all duration-300 relative group glow-card">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide font-sans">Buy, Borrow, Die</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Model Securities-Based Lines of Credit (SBLOC) vs. capital gains liquidation. Analyze margin call liquidation buffers and capital gains tax drag avoidance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a 
            href="/buy-borrow-die-calculator/" 
            class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-3 bg-[#00F5D4]/10 hover:bg-[#00F5D4] border border-[#00F5D4]/30 hover:border-transparent text-brand-300 hover:text-slate-950 font-bold text-xs rounded-xl tracking-wider uppercase transition-all duration-300 shadow-md shadow-[#00F5D4]/5"
          >
            Try the Buy, Borrow, Die Calculator
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: S-Corp Tax -->
      <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-[#00F5D4]/40 transition-all duration-300 relative group glow-card">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide font-sans">Side-Hustle S-Corp Tax</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Compare sole proprietorship taxes against corporate structures in the US, UK, Canada, and Australia. Run reasonable salary splits and overhead break-even audits.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a 
            href="/s-corp-tax-calculator/" 
            class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-3 bg-[#00F5D4]/10 hover:bg-[#00F5D4] border border-[#00F5D4]/30 hover:border-transparent text-brand-300 hover:text-slate-950 font-bold text-xs rounded-xl tracking-wider uppercase transition-all duration-300 shadow-md shadow-[#00F5D4]/5"
          >
            Try the S-Corp Tax Predictor
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Debt Payoff -->
      <div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-[#00F5D4]/40 transition-all duration-300 relative group glow-card">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-rose-500/10 border border-rose-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-rose-400">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide font-sans">Debt Payoff Planner</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Simulate Debt Snowball vs. Debt Avalanche strategies. Compare total interest costs, payoff times, and map monthly roll-over schedules to accelerate freedom.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a 
            href="/debt-payoff-calculator/" 
            class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-3 bg-[#00F5D4]/10 hover:bg-[#00F5D4] border border-[#00F5D4]/30 hover:border-transparent text-brand-300 hover:text-slate-950 font-bold text-xs rounded-xl tracking-wider uppercase transition-all duration-300 shadow-md shadow-[#00F5D4]/5"
          >
            Try the Debt Payoff Planner
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contextual Linking Paragraph -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-sans">
        Whether you are looking to model the tax benefits of the <a href="/buy-borrow-die-calculator/" class="text-[#00F5D4] hover:underline font-semibold">Buy, Borrow, Die strategy</a>, optimize your compensation split using our <a href="/s-corp-tax-calculator/" class="text-[#00F5D4] hover:underline font-semibold">S-Corp tax calculator</a>, or map a payoff schedule with the <a href="/debt-payoff-calculator/" class="text-[#00F5D4] hover:underline font-semibold">debt snowball vs avalanche planner</a>, our tools help you keep more of what you earn.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
